Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:39.99,Title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(500,0)}住慣了的話也是很舒心的櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:54.70,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}晴れ渡る空は青く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:01:00.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}近づいてくる足音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:06.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}浸りだした風に押されるように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:11.69,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}ほら　出会ってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}それぞれの夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:18.53,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}それぞれの未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:24.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}負けないように走り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:25.38,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}気づいたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:30.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}ずっと一緒にいたんだ　だれよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:36.50,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}悩んで落ち込んで　泣いて笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:40.12,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:46.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}君に届け　空をかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:51.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}まっすぐな思い　ぎゅっと抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:57.96,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}きっと　生まれたての強さは無限に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:03.37,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}この気持ちが翼になり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:10.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,500)}私はわたしのためで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:54.70,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}萬里晴空如此湛藍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:01:00.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}悄悄靠近著的腳步聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:06.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}像是被濕潤的風推搡著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:11.69,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}你看  我們相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.42,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}各自的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:18.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}各自的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:24.14,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}為了不輸給任何人我們奔跑著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:25.38,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}等察覺時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:30.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}已經一直在一起了  比任何人都要久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:36.50,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}煩惱著消沉著  哭泣  歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:40.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}然後加速
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:46.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}追逐著你  飛躍藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:51.62,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}緊緊擁抱那份執著的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:57.96,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}初生的力量一定是無限的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:03.37,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}我要將這份心情化為羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:10.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,500)}為了我自己勇敢前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:40.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}ありふれた感情から  卒業もできでなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.06,0:21:43.90,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}眠れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:51.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}突然の雨泥濘んだ  あの靴は瞬きする
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:57.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}キミの世界をきっと受け止めている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:04.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}君のリアル　僕の視線　どこか違うとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:11.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}あのくたびれたTシャツみたいにさせないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:18.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}PRIME NUMBER世界にどれひとつとして同じものがない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:25.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}心の空白を無理に埋めなくてもいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:32.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}たくさんの誰かの記憶に残されているよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:39.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,500)}屋根の上君だけの空になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:40.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}不能從那俗不可耐的感情中畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.06,0:21:43.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}無法入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:51.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}那雙鞋被突如其來的雨打濕而滿是泥濘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:57.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}一定已經全盤接受了你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:04.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}你的現實  我的視線  即使有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:11.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}也不會讓它變成那穿舊了的T恤一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:18.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}在素數的世界中  沒有一個是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:25.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}不用勉強去填補心中的空白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:32.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}比起在許多人心中留下記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:39.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,500)}我更想成為屋頂上那片只屬於你的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑大人現在不能接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請留言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是在這吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不好意思啊  把你叫到這種地方來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要坐中午的航班飛去舊金山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是去工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我在遊戲開發者大會有個演說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們趕緊開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼戰鬥的劇本就按現在的來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就只要做標題審查會上用的的企劃書了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新增的畫可以拜託畫這幅畫的女孩畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這種存在感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能追加上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想這對審查會是很有利的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我去問問椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一會還要去約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午是我妹妹的成績公佈會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊勒  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也要去工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個不想去參加的會議
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換做以往  她肯定會說「不如你代我去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這麼說  不過我換了衣服就得馬上出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是優子醬的成績公佈會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以和你一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下  我去換件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  為什麼連椎名也跟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子合格與否是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裏重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會影響到將來的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格的話會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,執行C計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好喜歡這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那換成B？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是交往的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交往？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青…青山…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太和七海臉好紅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生病了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  青山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試鏡的結果什麼時候出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽…聽說是二月底或是三月初
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太看起來好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海看起來也好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的吧  青山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又和青山卿卿我我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  很合拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綠燈了  走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  我有事要拜託椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想請你畫企劃書的畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我畫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  會不會影響到你畫漫畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我畫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太  你不高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  才沒有那種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子醬的准考證號是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,99…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你落榜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能  你再好好看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再仔細看也是落榜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九十幾號大家都考上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:05:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是沒有99號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼只有優子落榜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是你考試分數不理想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該對受傷的優子說些溫柔的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該什麼時候拉開「恭喜合格」的綵球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我三天前就開始做這東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綵球也掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那縣立高中的考試要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊勒？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟伊織參加了音樂科的入學考試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑沒和你們在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在三鷹正在學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？仁學長他？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向班主任報告他考試通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三鷹真的要拋下美笑去大阪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連情人節都沒能見上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在距離畢業只有兩個星期了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個星期…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們倆竟然就要這樣畢業了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一點都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山  去把美笑學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去把她帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了  我去拖住仁學長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得會成功嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天知道  我們可管不了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁學長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連小真白都一臉嚴肅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我們走一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷的愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要殺要剮隨你們啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我帶到這種地方來  有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不是什麼愛的告白之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是關於美笑學姐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙最近在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是美笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也會很快就忘記我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這話是真心的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是玩笑就能說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去大阪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請和美笑學姐好好談一談
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒辦法和美笑交往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁學長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還想讓我說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的仁學長一點都不像仁學長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼算是像我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直非常帥氣又睿智什麼事都得心應手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很成熟很可靠還能為我們排憂解難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我作為目標的仁學長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是空太沒眼光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會認為我會因為你和美笑學姐的事而放棄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是美笑學姐被別人搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}放手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和別人成為戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑學姐的所有都成為別的男人的東西也不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在問你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要自說自話了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是仁學長讓我說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事都能得心應手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很成熟很可靠  這是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也已經被壓得喘不過氣來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不知道大學能不能合格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻因為美笑的事完全不能集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對美笑告白  根本不是一件輕而易舉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是需要做好和美笑永遠在一起的覺悟的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就有這樣覺悟的仁學長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今還在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太  你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊  椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快能看到小褲褲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不能看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然敢堂堂正正的偷窺裙下風光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太也成長了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁學長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:09:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這麼喜歡的話就不要多想了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請和美笑學姐交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有聽我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑  馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山去叫她了  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上井草學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  精神百倍啊  七海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三鷹學長現在在學校裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以學姐和我一起去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在要完成這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要干咯  要好好幹咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣真的好嗎  上井草學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我不能隱藏自己的感情的可是上井草學姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:11:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可學姐卻要在一個地方繼續轉上幾百圈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑醬好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁  快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一直和仁在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪啦  打仗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來打雪仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來玩的人就抓住這隻手指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}美笑醬玩的話就不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為根本贏不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要打倒美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是男人的執著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直認為和仁在一起是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁  早上了哦起床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不起來的話  就給你早安的吻了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊看啊  怎麼樣啊這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千萬別在外面做這種事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不想被別人看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風…風香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑  要拍照咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快下來快下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家爸媽真是很寵美笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐很不滿這點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為連相機都買新的了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  你不換衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在等著風香出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然會在意我的視線  真是囂張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁  快點啦快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能早點察覺這份感情就好了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一學期結束紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人吃不消真吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不明白那種人頭腦為什麼會那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三鷹君  現在要回家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要去卡拉ok  要不要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有很多其他班的人會來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有比那傢伙更可愛的女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說今天我有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙感覺挺有料的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然性格真是不敢恭維啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓我們干一把麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,yeah  完成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是上井草啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿她沒轍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又打架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下是第幾次了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs19}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啊  風香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁的心臟跳得好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…彼此彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺已經看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁被美笑所傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:13:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛吃了一驚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不會傷害仁的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是早點能察覺的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不用原地打轉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁  風香醬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是美笑最喜歡的螃蟹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔阿姨叫你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑是不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她最近都在迴避我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迴避你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是美笑學姐她已經恢復活力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不接我電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不回我消息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以美笑是不會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊  害怕見到仁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果現在見面的話我可能會說些很過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我也想如果完成這個場景的話或許就能見他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但無論如何也完成不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為根本不想去完成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此美笑也會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海會帶著她過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…能進水高真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這裏啊上井草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是來說遺言的嗎  僊人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了  僊人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水明藝術大學附屬高等學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上井草啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個小小的城市裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不會有你這種外星人的同伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊  如果去了這個學校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許會遇到流浪到地球來的你的同伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去考考看這個學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候我才注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑也明白了自己是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁學長為什麼去考了水高了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想考水高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個笑話一點也不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠離父母的學生宿舍聽起來很讓人期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我對藝術大學也有點興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然仁也選擇了美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把美笑當做重要的人為她擔心著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只看著美笑一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以為只有仁會看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對仁來說  我只是美笑的替代品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為害怕傷害美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓純潔無瑕的她待在自己的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才會抱著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你多少也辯解一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底  還是放不下美笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  急死人了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次三鷹學長可是真的要遠行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的能讓他就這樣走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快飛向宇宙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…七海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能來水高真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能遇到你們真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能有你們這樣會為美笑而如此認真的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不會來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久…久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久…久等了  學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這邊也有很多原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁學長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你們稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說了叫你們開門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名也來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我衝過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…這是在推我？在給我撓癢？還是在揉我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是要鬧哪樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得哪個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我推
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上井草學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再用力些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  一群多管閒事的後輩們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  偶然這樣也不錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:18:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被大學錄取了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四月份就要去大阪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊  美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去做自己真正想做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭的時候和小真白他們一起做了喵波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就注意到了吧  很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白的作畫很厲害  每天都非常期待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小龍也能滿足我所有的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在是太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  你已經明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的劇本是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是坦白的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  仁的劇本不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓我有心跳的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  在我提交劇本的時候看上去非常失望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四年後  我會憑我的實力成為上井草美笑指名的劇本作家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…嘛…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是防狼的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要的話就扔掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…絕對不會摘下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們  跟我來一下教導處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下是指五分鐘可以嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我可要好好訓訓你們  給我做好覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的  知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年以來多謝關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我打開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後會被訓得更厲害的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正惹人家生氣的是空太嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們三年級是自由來校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天開始就不來學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連這點你都算計好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是櫻花莊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}（屋頂上還有人。巡邏的時候請注意！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海  真白  看啊看啊  鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來真的好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然繞了很多的遠路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.03,0:22:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你們兩個人悄悄的在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在說我們到底能走到哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.31,0:23:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論哪裏我們都能到達的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.27,0:23:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦  學弟君口氣不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在櫻花莊就會有這種想法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.58,0:23:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三鷹也在正好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天理事會決定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年之內櫻花莊就要被拆除了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.58,0:23:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊  小光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還不在時的櫻花莊是什麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.92,0:23:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘎吱嘎吱地十分繁茂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太也雖軟弱但繁盛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
